"""
Generic PNG -> Doom patch converter.

Features:
- Uses PLAYPAL from the WAD when available
- Falls back to bundled palette otherwise
- Preserves transparency
- Preserves grAb sprite offsets
- Converts arbitrary PNG graphics into Doom patch lumps
"""

